code: @Override public void setBeanFactory(BeanFactory beanFactory) throws BeansException {     this.beanFactory = beanFactory. }

@Override public void registerBeanDefinitions(AnnotationMetadata importingClassMetadata, final BeanDefinitionRegistry registry) {     super.registerBeanDefinitions(new StandardAnnotationMetadata(IntegrationComponentScanConfiguration.class, true), registry). }
